">Chapter Chronology</caption>\n\t\n\t<tbody>\n\t<tr>\n\t\n\t\t<td class=\"pi-horizontal-group-item pi-data-value pi-font pi-border-color pi-item-spacing\">← <a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_153\" title=\"Chapter 153\">Previous</a></td>\n\t\n\t\t<td class=\"pi-horizontal-group-item pi-data-value pi-font pi-border-color pi-item-spacing\"><a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_155\" title=\"Chapter 155\">Next</a> →</td>\n\t\n\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n</section>\n</aside>\n\n</p><p><b>Chapter 154</b> is titled \"To Arabasta\".\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Cover_Page\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Cover Page</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Short_Summary\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Short Summary</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Long_Summary\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Long Summary</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quick_Reference\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quick Reference</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Chapter_Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chapter Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Characters\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Characters</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Author_Comment\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Author Comment</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Site_Navigation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Site Navigation</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Cover_Page\">Cover Page</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_154%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D1&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Jango%27s_Dance_Paradise\" title=\"Jango&#39;s Dance Paradise\">Jango's Dance Paradise</a>, Vol. 22: \"The Power of a Marine Headquarters Lieutenant\".\n</p><p><a href=\"/wiki/Fullbody\" title=\"Fullbody\">Fullbody</a> goes into action, crushing the <a href=\"/wiki/Tulip_Pirates\" title=\"Tulip Pirates\">Tulip Pirates</a> almost singlehandedly.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Short_Summary\">Short Summary</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_154%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D2&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>While <a href=\"/wiki/Kureha\" title=\"Kureha\">Kureha</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Dalton\" title=\"Dalton\">Dalton</a> rejoice about the now possible rebirth of their country, they learn that <a href=\"/wiki/Tony_Tony_Chopper\" title=\"Tony Tony Chopper\">Chopper</a> has joined a group of pirates whose captain is worth <span style=\"white-space:nowrap;\"><span class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Belly\" title=\"Belly\"><img src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/d/de/Beli.png/revision/latest?cb=20141206091723\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"12\" height=\"20\" class=\"mw-file-element\" data-image-name=\"Beli.png\" data-image-key=\"Beli.png\" data-relevant=\"0\" /></a></span></span>30,000,000. Meanwhile, Chopper discovers the life on board the <a href=\"/wiki/Going_Merry\" title=\"Going Merry\">Going Merry</a> with his new friends.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Long_Summary\">Long Summary</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_154%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D3&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Kureha\" title=\"Kureha\">Kureha</a> and Dalton are sitting under the sakura snow, now full of hope about the future of their country when a villager appears carrying <a href=\"/wiki/Monkey_D._Luffy\" title=\"Monkey D. Luffy\">Luffy</a>'s bounty poster. Understanding their friend has encountered some dangerous people, Kureha makes mysterious remarks about <a href=\"/wiki/Gol_D._Roger\" title=\"Gol D. Roger\">Gol D. Roger</a> and the <a href=\"/wiki/Will_of_D.\" title=\"Will of D.\">Will of D.</a> When asked about where the poster came from, the villager replies that a few days ago, a stranger appeared, looking for the <a href=\"/wiki/Blackbeard_Pirates\" title=\"Blackbeard Pirates\">Blackbeard Pirates</a> who destroyed the island. When the stranger called <a href=\"/wiki/Portgas_D._Ace\" title=\"Portgas D. Ace\">Ace</a> learned that they have already left, he gave Luffy's poster to the villagers so that, in case he reaches <a href=\"/wiki/Drum_Island\" title=\"Drum Island\">Drum</a>, they can tell Luffy he would wait for him in <a href=\"/wiki/Arabasta\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Arabasta\">Arabasta</a> for 10 days.\n</p><p>Onboard the <a href=\"/wiki/Going_Merry\" title=\"Going Merry\">Going Merry</a>, Chopper is full of nostalgia and does not rejoice with the others, who are having a sakura party. However, once <a href=\"/wiki/Nami\" title=\"Nami\">Nami</a> gives him his medicine bag, which he had no time to prepare during his hasty departure, he understands that Kureha did it for him, secretly agreeing with his departure. This revelation changes his mood and he quickly learns the crew's customs who happily celebrate the new Straw Hats' doctor.\n</p><p>Meanwhile in <a href=\"/wiki/Little_Garden\" title=\"Little Garden\">Little Garden</a>, an <a href=\"/wiki/Okama\" title=\"Okama\">okama</a> named <a href=\"/wiki/Bentham\" title=\"Bentham\">Mr. 2</a> is searching for <a href=\"/wiki/Galdino\" title=\"Galdino\">Mr. 3</a> in order to accomplish <a href=\"/wiki/Crocodile\" title=\"Crocodile\">Crocodile</a>'s orders to kill him, but Mr. 3 is nowhere to be found.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quick_Reference\">Quick Reference</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_154%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D4&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chapter_Notes\">Chapter Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_154%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D5&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li>Dr. <a href=\"/wiki/Kureha\" title=\"Kureha\">Kureha</a> mentions the <a href=\"/wiki/Will_of_D.\" title=\"Will of D.\">Will of D.</a> for the first time.</li>\n<li>Gold Roger's real name was <a href=\"/wiki/Gol_D._Roger\" title=\"Gol D. Roger\">Gol D. Roger</a>.</li>\n<li>A few days ago, a stranger named <a href=\"/wiki/Portgas_D._Ace\" title=\"Portgas D. Ace\">Ace</a> arrived on <a href=\"/wiki/Drum_Island\" title=\"Drum Island\">Drum Island</a> on a day when it did not snow.\n<ul><li>Ace told the citizens to tell <a href=\"/wiki/Monkey_D._Luffy\" title=\"Monkey D. Luffy\">Luffy</a> that he will be waiting in <a href=\"/wiki/Arabasta\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Arabasta\">Arabasta</a> for ten days.</li>\n<li>Ace is also looking for the <a href=\"/wiki/Blackbeard_Pirates\" title=\"Blackbeard Pirates\">Blackbeard Pirates</a>.</li></ul></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Bentham\" title=\"Bentham\">Mr. 2</a> is fully seen for the first time</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Crocodile\" title=\"Crocodile\">Crocodile</a> decides to head into Alabasta to show his position as the kingdom's hero.</li>\n<li>This is the last chapter of the <a href=\"/wiki/Drum_Island_Arc\" title=\"Drum Island Arc\">Drum Island Arc</a>.</li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Characters\">Characters</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_154%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D6&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<table class=\"CharTable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/Pirate\" title=\"Pirate\">Pirates</a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/Marines\" title=\"Marines\">Marines</a>\n</th>\n<th>Citizens\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/Baroque_Works\" title=\"Baroque Works\">Baroque Works</a>\n</th>\n<th>Others\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Straw_Hat_Pirates\" title=\"Straw Hat Pirates\">Straw Hat Pirates</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Monkey_D._Luffy\" title=\"Monkey D. Luffy\">Monkey D. Luffy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Roronoa_Zoro\" title=\"Roronoa Zoro\">Roronoa Zoro</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Nami\" title=\"Nami\">Nami</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Usopp\" title=\"Usopp\">Usopp</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Sanji\" title=\"Sanji\">Sanji</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Tony_Tony_Chopper\" title=\"Tony Tony Chopper\">Tony Tony Chopper</a></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td>\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Marine_Ranks#Lieutenant\" title=\"Marine Ranks\">Lieutenant</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Fullbody\" title=\"Fullbody\">Fullbody</a> (cover)</li></ul>\n</td>\n<td>\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Drum_Island\" title=\"Drum Island\">Drum Island</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Dalton\" title=\"Dalton\">Dalton</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Kureha\" title=\"Kureha\">Kureha</a></li></ul>\n<hr />\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Arabasta\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Arabasta\">Arabasta</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Nefertari_Vivi\" title=\"Nefertari Vivi\">Nefertari Vivi</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Karoo\" title=\"Karoo\">Karoo</a></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Crocodile\" title=\"Crocodile\">Crocodile</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Nico_Robin\" title=\"Nico Robin\">Miss All Sunday</a></li></ul>\n<hr />\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Baroque_Works#Members\" title=\"Baroque Works\">Officer Agents</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Bentham\" title=\"Bentham\">Mr. 2 Bon Kurei</a></li></ul>\n<hr />\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Baroque_Works#Billions\" title=\"Baroque Works\">Billions</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Akumai\" title=\"Akumai\">Akumai</a></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Portgas_D._Ace\" title=\"Portgas D. Ace\">Ace</a>&#160;(flashback)</li></ul>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Author_Comment\">Author Comment</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_154%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D7&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><br />\n</p><table class=\"wikitable\" style=\"margin: auto; text-align: center; width:50%\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/List_of_WSJ_Author_Comments\" title=\"List of WSJ Author Comments\">Author Comment</a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:90%\"><div class=\"tabber wds-tabber\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__wrapper with-bottom-border\"><ul class=\"wds-tabs\"><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab wds-is-current\" data-hash=\"Translation\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Translation</a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"Original\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Original</a></div></li></ul></div><div class=\"wds-tab__content wds-is-current\"><p><br />\nThe snow country arc is finished. Phe~~w I sure drew a heckuva lot of 'em, 'circles'. Well, up next is a kingdom of sand so I guess it's on to 'dots'.*</p></div><div class=\"wds-tab__content\"><p><br />\n雪国編が終わりました。は～～しかし描いたな～“丸”。次は砂の王国なので“点”だな</p></div></div>—<a href=\"/wiki/Eiichiro_Oda\" title=\"Eiichiro Oda\">Eiichiro Oda</a></td><td><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Eiichiro_Oda\" title=\"Eiichiro Oda\"><img src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/a/ad/Eiichiro_Oda_WSJ_Avatar.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20230801133230\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" class=\"mw-file-element\" data-image-name=\"Eiichiro Oda WSJ Avatar.png\" data-image-key=\"Eiichiro_Oda_WSJ_Avatar.png\" data-relevant=\"1\" /></a></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"><i>English translation by <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.thegrandline.com/odatocLIVE.htm\">Greg Werner</a>. For comprehensive translation credits, see <a href=\"/wiki/List_of_WSJ_Author_Comments#Translation_Credits\" title=\"List of WSJ Author Comments\">here</a>.</i></td></tr>\n\n</tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Site_Navigation\">Site Navigation</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_154%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D8&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds